### Token Insight & Analytics API Test File
# You can run these requests directly using VS Code extensions like "REST Client" or "HTTPYac"

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

---

### 1. Token Insight API
# Retrieves market data for a given token from CoinGecko and analyzes it using the configured AI model.

# cURL Equivalent:
# curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/api/token/chainlink/insight \
#      -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
#      -d '{"vs_currency": "usd", "history_days": 30}'

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/token/chainlink/insight
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vs_currency": "aave",
  "history_days": 7
}

###

### 2. HyperLiquid Wallet Daily PnL API
# Retrieves historical trades and funding for a given HyperLiquid wallet address and calculates daily PnL.

# cURL Equivalent:
# curl -X GET "http://localhost:3000/api/hyperliquid/0x0000000000000000000000000000000000000000/pnl?start=2024-01-01&end=2025-01-01"

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/hyperliquid/0x0000000000000000000000000000000000000000/pnl?start=2024-01-01&end=2025-01-01
